description: "On this beautifully illustrated and coloured map of Java, mountains, trees, fields of crops and settlements are shown pictorially. The coasts are marked with shoals, reefs, bathymetry (sea depth, in figures) and anchor points."
title: "Nieuwe en zeer naaukeurige kaart van t eyland Java Major of Groot Java : verdeeld in seven byzondere bostekken / door François Valentyn V.D.M. ;  J et G. Onder de Linden excudnt."
